data.description: Needs some work and updating, but regardless you'll love the welcoming rustic interior this home offers. Cute and cozy with log cabin accents. The main living area features high, vaulted wooden ceilings and a fireplace, creating a sense of being in the North Woods. Most walls have natural wood paneling that gives the space a warm and inviting ambiance. Adjacent to the living room is a small den. It's possible to remove the wall to have a larger living space. The hardwood floors have character and its vintage feel adds to the home's charm. Upstairs is a loft master bedroom and bath. Many newer features include a new hot water heater, and stackable washer/dryer. The siding has been updated. Being sold "as-is." Located on a large wooded lot with woods and a stream behind the property. Huge detached garage and an ideal setting makes this property a great place to come home to.
